FeedPackage.Description:
Bytescout Spreadsheet SDK for .NET, ASP.NET, ActiveX, VB6 Command Line console
(c) ByteScout 2006-2013
Read XLS, Write XLS, Calculate XLS with this SDK from your .NET and ASP.NET applications Bytescout Spreadsheet SDK writes, reads, calculates and converts spreadsheets (XLS, XLSX, CSV, TXT, ODS)
- No Excel or Office installed are required! - Formula calculation support (Excel style formulas) - Writes to XLS, XLSX, HTML, CSV, TXT, XML formats - Reads XLS, XLSX (MS Excel 2007), ODS (Open Office Calc), CSV, TXT formats - Supports cell formating, rich text, charts, images, borders etc - Includes support for Compact Framework .NET (Windows CE and Pocket PC) - Includes ActiveX legacy languages support like Visual Basic 6, VBScript, Javascript, ASP - Command line is included for conversion of spreadsheet files from command line or .BAT files - and more!
http://bytescout.com/products/developer/spreadsheetsdk/bytescoutspreadsheetsdk.html

FeedPackage.Title: Bytescout.Spreadsheet

FeedPackage.Description:
Bytescout Spreadsheet SDK for .NET, ASP.NET, ActiveX, VB6 Command Line console
(c) ByteScout 2006-2015
Read XLS, Write XLS, Calculate XLS with this SDK from your .NET and ASP.NET applications Bytescout Spreadsheet SDK writes, reads, calculates and converts spreadsheets (XLS, XLSX, CSV, TXT, ODS)
- No Excel or Office installed are required! - Formula calculation support (Excel style formulas) - Writes to XLS, XLSX, HTML, CSV, TXT, XML formats - Reads XLS, XLSX (MS Excel 2007), ODS (Open Office Calc), CSV, TXT formats - Supports cell formating, rich text, charts, images, borders etc - Includes support for Compact Framework .NET (Windows CE and Pocket PC) - Includes ActiveX legacy languages support like Visual Basic 6, VBScript, Javascript, ASP - Command line is included for conversion of spreadsheet files from command line or .BAT files - and more!
http://bytescout.com/products/developer/spreadsheetsdk/bytescoutspreadsheetsdk.html

FeedPackage.Description:
Bytescout Spreadsheet SDK for .NET, ASP.NET, ActiveX, VB6 Command Line console
(c) ByteScout 2006-2015
Read XLS, Write XLS, Calculate XLS with this SDK from your .NET and ASP.NET applications Bytescout Spreadsheet SDK writes, reads, calculates and converts spreadsheets (XLS, XLSX, CSV, TXT, ODS)
- No Excel or Office installed are required! - Formula calculation support (Excel style formulas) - Writes to XLS, XLSX, HTML, CSV, TXT, XML formats - Reads XLS, XLSX (MS Excel 2007), ODS (Open Office Calc), CSV, TXT formats - Supports cell formating, rich text, charts, images, borders etc - Includes support for Compact Framework .NET (Windows CE and Pocket PC) - Includes ActiveX legacy languages support like Visual Basic 6, VBScript, Javascript, ASP - Command line is included for conversion of spreadsheet files from command line or .BAT files - and more!
http://bytescout.com/products/developer/spreadsheetsdk/bytescoutspreadsheetsdk.html

FeedPackage.Title: Bytescout.Spreadsheet

FeedPackage.Description:
Bytescout Spreadsheet SDK for .NET, ASP.NET, ActiveX, VB6 Command Line console
(c) ByteScout 2006-2016
Read XLS, Write XLS, Calculate XLS with this SDK from your .NET and ASP.NET applications Bytescout Spreadsheet SDK writes, reads, calculates and converts spreadsheets (XLS, XLSX, CSV, TXT, ODS)
- No Excel or Office installed are required! - Formula calculation support (Excel style formulas) - Writes to XLS, XLSX, HTML, CSV, TXT, XML formats - Reads XLS, XLSX (MS Excel 2007), ODS (Open Office Calc), CSV, TXT formats - Supports cell formating, rich text, charts, images, borders etc - Includes support for Compact Framework .NET (Windows CE and Pocket PC) - Includes ActiveX legacy languages support like Visual Basic 6, VBScript, Javascript, ASP - Command line is included for conversion of spreadsheet files from command line or .BAT files - and more!
http://bytescout.com/products/developer/spreadsheetsdk/bytescoutspreadsheetsdk.html

FeedPackage.Title: Bytescout.Spreadsheet

FeedPackage.Description:
Bytescout Spreadsheet SDK for .NET, ASP.NET, ActiveX, VB6 Command Line console
(c) ByteScout 2006-2016
Read XLS, Write XLS, Calculate XLS with this SDK from your .NET and ASP.NET applications Bytescout Spreadsheet SDK writes, reads, calculates and converts spreadsheets (XLS, XLSX, CSV, TXT, ODS)
- No Excel or Office installed are required! - Formula calculation support (Excel style formulas) - Writes to XLS, XLSX, HTML, CSV, TXT, XML formats - Reads XLS, XLSX (MS Excel 2007), ODS (Open Office Calc), CSV, TXT formats - Supports cell formating, rich text, charts, images, borders etc - Includes support for Compact Framework .NET (Windows CE and Pocket PC) - Includes ActiveX legacy languages support like Visual Basic 6, VBScript, Javascript, ASP - Command line is included for conversion of spreadsheet files from command line or .BAT files - and more!
http://bytescout.com/products/developer/spreadsheetsdk/bytescoutspreadsheetsdk.html

FeedPackage.Title: Bytescout.Spreadsheet

FeedPackage.Description:
Bytescout Spreadsheet SDK for .NET, ASP.NET, ActiveX, VB6 Command Line console
(c) ByteScout 2006-2016
Read XLS, Write XLS, Calculate XLS with this SDK from your .NET and ASP.NET applications Bytescout Spreadsheet SDK writes, reads, calculates and converts spreadsheets (XLS, XLSX, CSV, TXT, ODS)
- No Excel or Office installed are required! - Formula calculation support (Excel style formulas) - Writes to XLS, XLSX, HTML, CSV, TXT, XML formats - Reads XLS, XLSX (MS Excel 2007), ODS (Open Office Calc), CSV, TXT formats - Supports cell formating, rich text, charts, images, borders etc - Includes support for Compact Framework .NET (Windows CE and Pocket PC) - Includes ActiveX legacy languages support like Visual Basic 6, VBScript, Javascript, ASP - Command line is included for conversion of spreadsheet files from command line or .BAT files - and more!
http://bytescout.com/products/developer/spreadsheetsdk/bytescoutspreadsheetsdk.html
